OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FITV Border will be sitting down with
OL,7,Fall the main political party leaders
OL,8,Fduring the Holyrood election campaign.
OL,10,FThe second interview was with Scottish
OL,11,FLabour's Anas Sarwar. Here are three
OL,12,Fthings we learned.
OL,14,FHe doesn't want to be Mr Glasgow...
OL,15,Fwhen he's outside the central belt
OL,17,FLabour's election strategy is clear
OL,18,Fand has been a long time in the
OL,19,Fplanning.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FThe party is targeting constituencies
OL,7,Facross Scotland's central belt and
OL,8,Fparts of the west coast in the hope it
OL,9,Fcan turn out a concentrated patch of
OL,10,Fsupport that allows it to perform
OL,11,Fabove top line polling numbers.
OL,13,FLet's leave aside for a second the
OL,14,Ffact that current polling has them so
OL,15,Ffar behind the SNP to make the
OL,16,Fstrategy look extremely optimistic at
OL,17,Fbest unless there is a marked shift
OL,18,Fover the next four weeks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FThere's an obvious downside to this
OL,7,Fstrategy. That's the fact it means
OL,8,FLabour focuses heavily on a small
OL,9,Fgeographical area of Scotland, albeit
OL,10,Fone that's home to the vast majority
OL,11,Fof the country's population.
OL,13,FMr Sarwar was at pains to be seen as a
OL,14,Fleader who can talk to the whole of
OL,15,FScotland and carefully chose his
OL,16,Flanguage to strike a chord with the
OL,17,Ffrustrations of many in the south of
OL,18,FScotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FHe said: "It feels like for many
OL,7,Fpeople across the communities in the
OL,8,FBorders and Dumfries and Galloway that
OL,9,Fthey've been forgotten about.
OL,11,F"Forgotten about when it comes to
OL,12,Faccess to health services and too many
OL,13,Fpeople waiting far too long.
OL,15,F"Forgotten about in terms of young
OL,16,Fpeople getting the skills they need,
OL,17,For the training they need or the jobs
OL,18,Fthey need."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FThe question is whether he or his team
OL,7,Fwill maintain focus on these areas
OL,8,Fwhen they have to compete with the
OL,9,Fdemands of Glasgow's hospital scandal
OL,10,Fand other issues on Mr Sarwar's home
OL,11,Fturf.
OL,13,FLabour has policies for the south of
OL,14,FScotland
OL,16,FMr Sarwar argued that suggestions he
OL,17,Fhas a central belt bias are unfounded
OL,18,Fand his allies point to two policies
OL,19,Fhe announced as proof that Labour is
OL,20,Fthinking about our region.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FThe first was pledging to fully dual
OL,7,Fboth the A75 and A77, which are two of
OL,8,FScotland's key trunk roads that local
OL,9,Fcouncils say urgently need upgraded.
OL,11,FThe A75 runs from Gretna to Stranraer
OL,12,Fwhile the A77 goes down the Ayrshire
OL,13,Fcoast but both serve the ports at
OL,14,FCairnryan, which is the main point of
OL,15,Fentry or exit for heavy goods vehicles
OL,16,Fheading to or from Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FAs such, they are seen as crucial to
OL,7,Fthe economy of the whole UK given it
OL,8,Fis essentially a gateway to the
OL,9,FEuropean Union because of the ability
OL,10,Fto easily move from Belfast to the
OL,11,FRepublic of Ireland.
OL,13,FMr Sarwar said: "We will for the first
OL,14,Ftime have a proper business case for
OL,15,Fthe A77/75. How we look at the
OL,16,Feconomic opportunities of course, how
OL,17,Fwe look at safety because there's been
OL,18,Ffar too many instances of fatalities
OL,19,Fand injuries and collisions on the A77
OL,20,Fand the A75.
OL,26,@uD@QOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,F"But also the connectivity, how the
OL,7,Fsouth of Scotland can connect yes to
OL,8,Fthe central belt but also with
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, which is a huge part
OL,10,Fof the economic potential for
OL,11,FScotland."
OL,13,FHe was unable to say how much the
OL,14,Fproject would cost or how long it
OL,15,Fwould take, which will inevitably
OL,16,Fraise eyebrows despite his insistence
OL,17,Fthat it needs the business case to be
OL,18,Fcompleted for any plan to be credible.
OL,26,@sD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatve manifesto has
OL,7,Fpromised to dual "key sections" of the
OL,8,FA75 within five years.
OL,10,FEarlier this week, the South West
OL,11,FScotland Transport Alliance identified
OL,12,Fa list of upgrades - nine on the A75
OL,13,Fand 11 on the A77 - that it says could
OL,14,Fbe realistically delivered in the
OL,15,Fcoming years.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
