PN,35610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FTransport secretary Fiona Hyslop last
OL,7,Fyear asked the alliance, which is led
OL,8,Fby Stena Line, P&O Ferries and Belfast
OL,9,FHarbour, to identify strategically-
OL,10,Fimportant work that could be carried
OL,11,Fout quickly.
OL,13,FMr Sarwar also promised to bring back
OL,14,Fmaternity services in Stranraer with
OL,15,Fwomen having to travel 70 miles to
OL,16,Fgive birth or in some cases deliver
OL,17,Ftheir babies themselves.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
