CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FThis has led to concerns being raised
OL,7,Fby Scotland's paitent safety
OL,8,Fcommissioner and first minister John
OL,9,FSwinney has pledged to consider the
OL,10,Fissue.
OL,12,FBut Mr Sarwar found himself in hot
OL,13,Fwater and was forced to apologise to
OL,14,Flocal campaigner Claire Fleming after
OL,15,Fa Labour leaflet was delivered to
OL,16,Fhomes featuring her picture and a made-
OL,17,Fup quote.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
