PN,35612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FIt will be interesting to see how full
OL,7,For detailed the promised separate
OL,8,Fsouth of Scotland manifesto will be
OL,9,Fwhen it is released.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer is still a sore point
OL,13,FIt has been almost exactly two weeks
OL,14,Fsince Anas Sarwar called on Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer to quit as prime minister.
OL,17,FNothing has changed in the intervening
OL,18,Fweeks, not even in the polls, which
OL,19,FScottish Labour blames on the person
OL,20,Fstill residing in Downing Street.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FMr Sarwar remains determined to be his
OL,7,Fown man and run a distinct campaign to
OL,8,Fbe first minister that does not rely
OL,9,Fon the UK government.
OL,11,FHere was his short pitch: "Let's make
OL,12,FScotland better right now, let's make
OL,13,Fan NHS that works, let's guarantee
OL,14,Fopportunities for young people, let's
OL,15,Fspend public money well."
OL,17,FDoes that remind you of anything?
OL,26,@sD@[OUwD@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FAbout six weeks out from the 2024 UK
OL,7,Fgeneral election, this is what Starmer
OL,8,Fhad to say to voters: "We can deliver
OL,9,Feconomic stability. Cut the NHS
OL,10,Fwaiting times. Secure our borders with
OL,11,Fa New Border Security Command. Harness
OL,12,FGreat British Energy to cut your bills
OL,13,Ffor good. Tackle anti-social
OL,14,Fbehaviour. And get the teachers we
OL,15,Fneed in your children's classroom."
OL,17,FYou might be thinking, well yes, it's
OL,18,Ftwo Labour leaders so of course their
OL,19,Fpitches to voters will be similar.
OL,26,@pD@WOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FBut given Mr Sarwar has called on
OL,7,FStarmer to go, I asked him what he
OL,8,Fwould do differently to the prime
OL,9,Fminister if he made it to high office.
OL,11,FI put the question to him four times
OL,12,Fdirectly and twice in a roundabout way.
OL,14,FIt's maybe worth quoting the end of
OL,15,Fthat exchange in full, which started
OL,16,Fwith me pointing out to Mr Sarwar that
OL,17,Fhis pitch was quite similar to
OL,18,FStarmer's.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FMr Sarwar: "Well I'm standing to be
OL,7,Ffirst minister and the choice to be
OL,8,Ffirst minister is between me and John
OL,9,FSwinney.
OL,11,F"And there might be those who want to
OL,12,Fobsess about who the occupant in
OL,13,FDowning Street is or who the UK
OL,14,Fgovernment is..."
OL,16,FInterviewer: "Well I just wondered
OL,17,Fbecause I started by asking what you
OL,18,Fwould do differently and you're making
OL,19,Fa very similar pitch, which many
OL,20,Fpeople would want that pitch, but I
OL,21,Fjust wonder how you're going to do it."
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOUvD@QO]xD@NOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,FMr Sarwar: "Well I'm telling you, I've
OL,7,Ftold you. We will cut waiting lists by
OL,8,Fmaking sure we are using capacity
OL,9,Fwherever it exists. We'll embrace
OL,10,Ftechnology for faster treatment,
OL,11,Ffaster diagnosis.
OL,13,F"We'll get things built in this
OL,14,Fcountry by reforming our planning
OL,15,Fsystem so we get faster decisions.
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,F"We will make sure we're supporting
OL,7,Four town centres and high streets by
OL,8,Fabolishing the unfair business rates
OL,9,Fschemes so we can re-reg the system in
OL,10,Ffavour of retail and hospitality in
OL,11,Ftown centres and high streets.
OL,13,F"We'll make sure we're respecting the
OL,14,Fpublic purse so we aren't wasting
OL,15,Fmoney, so we can drive down taxes in
OL,16,Fthe next parliament.
OL,18,F"And we're going to make sure we
OL,19,Fdeliver the best of our country,
OL,20,FScotland. And that's the big
OL,21,Fdifference between me and John Swinney.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G18/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776093067
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Anas
OL,4,CSarwar leader interview
OL,6,F"John Swinney thinks this is as good
OL,7,Fas it gets. He's had 20 years. I know
OL,8,Fwe can do better as a country,
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,F"We have the talent, we have the
OL,12,Fpeople, we have the resources, we have
OL,13,Fthe ideas. What we don't have is the
OL,14,Fgovernment to match it."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@XO]
